SPA - Single Page Application
.NET NET CORE 8 CLI, SOLIDJS-TYPESCRIPT (typescript) and IBM DB2 11.5.8.0 start-up project

Requirements:
1. Knowledge of C# API and SolidJs - TypeScript
2. Node 23.5.0 and NPM 11.1.0
3. IBM DB2 Docker Container
4. Bootstrap 5.3.7, JQuery and Axios
5. Visual Studio Code
6. Install Google or Microsoft Authenticator in your Mobile Phone

Features :
1. Authentication and Authorization
   BryCrypt, JWT
2. TimeBased One Time Password Authenticator or MFA
3. User Profile Picture upload/update
4. Product Listings and Pagination
5. User Account Activation via Email
6. Auto Mapper Dependency Injection
7. Swagger RESTful API Documentation
   https://localhost:7101/swagger/

If you want to test, do the following:
1. Setup IBM DB2 11.5.8.0 Docker container
2. Change Username and Password in appsettings.json, ORACLE connection settings
